OL,4,CGreen plan to upgrade homes was
OL,5,C'botched', say MPs
OL,6, The masterplan to help people upgrade
OL,7, the UK's homes has been "botched" and
OL,8, must be urgently overhauled, MPs say.
OL,10,FThe Business Select Committee says that
OL,11,Fthe Green Homes Grant (GHG), which
OL,12,Foffers people up to #10,000 for
OL,13,Finsulation, is so inept that it is
OL,14,Factually damaging the building sector.
OL,16,FIt adds that 19 million UK homes are
OL,17,Fpoorly insulated and accuses ministers
OL,18,Fof "failing to grasp" the challenge.
OL,20,FThe government says it is "committed to
OL,21,Fgoing further and faster".
